scope_of_work.scope:
WSP will perform a building condition assessment that aims to
— Promptly identify the major or “red flag” issues so that they are addressed appropriately;
— Explain and justify any recommendations;
— Develop a plan based on a prudent but reasonable management approach; and
— Clearly identify discretionary projects.

